88
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,200
We're the fairies of the forest!

89
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,930
Yes, we're fairies!

90
00:05:56,020 --> 00:05:57,870
Everyone!

91
00:05:57,870 --> 00:06:00,240
Nagi Nagi Stretch is starting!

92
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:09,430
But why did you build such
an amazing amusement park in the house?

93
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:12,640
