94
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,920
Old man...

95
00:06:15,260 --> 00:06:17,820
That person I met...

96
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:23,710
What's wrong, Hayate?

97
00:06:23,710 --> 00:06:24,700
N-No, nothing.

98
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:28,160
But, a birthday present, huh?

99
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:30,980
I guess he's a good grandfather to you.

100
00:06:30,980 --> 00:06:32,700
Do you really think so?

101
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:33,910
He isn't?

102
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:37,910
If you really think so, then take a good look around.

103
00:06:37,910 --> 00:06:39,510
Good look?

104
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:42,780
