a minimum height restriction of 140cm.

106
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,590
A minimum of 140cm!

107
00:06:47,590 --> 00:06:49,390
And another of 140cm!

108
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:53,190
So I can't ride most of the rides here.

109
00:06:53,190 --> 00:06:55,790
It's a very expensive prank.

110
00:06:56,260 --> 00:07:00,260
That old man would never do anything that would make me happy.

111
00:07:00,260 --> 00:07:01,500
That's why I hate him.

112
00:07:03,150 --> 00:07:07,970
She's still small and can't ride, but you can, right?

113
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:09,710
Everyone, come over here!

114
00:07:09,710 --> 00:07:12,440
We have the first person to ride the rides!

115
00:07:12,650 --> 00:07:13,480
Eh?

116
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,640
EH?!

117
00:07:20,130 --> 00:07:21,600
Are you all right, Hayate?

118
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:25,390
Yes, but I'd prefer something a little more safe next time.

119
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:28,360
Then how about the Haunted House?

120
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,650
Haunted House?

121
00:07:29,650 --> 00:07:30,730
That sounds good.

122
00:07:30,730 --> 00:07:32,530
That doesn't have a height restriction.

123
00:07:32,530 --> 00:07:34,990
No! W-W-W-What are you saying?

124
00:07:34,990 --> 00:07:38,240
T-T-T-The Haunted House is scary!

125
00:07:38,470 --> 00:07:41,080
Well, that's what Haunted Houses are made for.

126
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,760
No, I'm not scared.

127
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:44,240
I'm not scared, you hear?

128
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:47,910
But... it's dangerous if there's a hole in the floor.

129
00:07:47,910 --> 00:07:51,840
This isn't good. At this rate, they'll skip the Haunted House.

130
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,560
Waste of all the practice.

131
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:57,620
But we might get fired if we make her cry.

132
00:07:57,620 --> 00:07:58,860
That'd be a problem.

133
00:07:59,300 --> 00:08:02,840
I'll go check if there's anything dangerous.

134
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:04,900
If you insist so much.

135
00:08:05,470 --> 00:08:06,790
He's entering....

136
00:08:06,790 --> 00:08:08,410
Alone?

137
00:08:08,410 --> 00:08:09,810
All by himself?

138
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:12,330
Then we'll trip him up.

139
00:08:12,330 --> 00:08:14,170
We are?

140
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:15,990
I'll be off then.

141
00:08:15,990 --> 00:08:17,890
Take care, all right?

142
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:24,050
Wow, they made a really good one.

143
00:08:24,570 --> 00:08:25,860
It really is amazing.

144
