159
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,540
That's because...

160
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:22,110
...I have a grudge against you, I guess.

161
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,890
Y-You're!

162
00:09:25,020 --> 00:09:26,480
Who were you?

163
00:09:27,490 --> 00:09:30,050
You don't remember me?!

164
00:09:30,050 --> 00:09:34,810
I don't know who you are,
but what grudge do you hold against me?

165
00:09:34,810 --> 00:09:36,950
I won't forgive you.

166
00:09:36,950 --> 00:09:37,610
Click.

167
00:09:39,770 --> 00:09:43,740
You can't see me in this dark, can you?

168
00:09:44,420 --> 00:09:46,730
I'll be moving to your side now.

169
00:09:46,730 --> 00:09:47,300
Damn it.

170
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:51,170
Can you handle the pressure?

171
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:56,890
