172
00:09:56,890 --> 00:09:58,990
You're right; I won't be scared with this.

173
00:09:58,990 --> 00:10:00,810
Hayate! You're safe!

174
00:10:00,810 --> 00:10:01,610
Y-Yes.

175
00:10:02,090 --> 00:10:04,080
