176
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:07,850
I don't know what that is, but it's a very ugly robot.

177
00:10:07,850 --> 00:10:09,050
Y-You...

178
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:10,660
...little brat!

179
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:11,890
Die!

180
00:10:12,130 --> 00:10:14,090
Milady! Watch out!

181
00:10:15,260 --> 00:10:18,970
