188
00:10:37,780 --> 00:10:38,520
No clue.

189
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:41,770
Milady.

190
00:10:42,970 --> 00:10:43,990
Let us go on.

191
00:10:43,990 --> 00:10:46,010
