227
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,430
Insert.

228
00:13:20,330 --> 00:13:24,450
Spin spin spin spin.

229
00:13:27,710 --> 00:13:32,020
Now that debt-ridden butler isn't my rival.

230
00:13:32,020 --> 00:13:32,940
Hey!

231
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,540
You robot there!

232
00:13:35,540 --> 00:13:38,260
What company's spy are you?

233
00:13:38,260 --> 00:13:39,160
M-Makimura-san.

234
00:13:39,700 --> 00:13:42,430
Even you forgot about me?

235
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:47,470
Wait!

236
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:52,010
That robot looks familiar.

237
00:13:53,650 --> 00:13:56,860
Damn it... Makimura-san, please wait for me.

238
00:13:56,860 --> 00:13:58,820
I'll... I'll definitely...

239
00:13:59,150 --> 00:14:02,790
Maria, today was really, really fun!

240
00:14:03,050 --> 00:14:07,620
Hayate would go wham and bam!

241
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:08,580
Yes, yes.

242
00:14:08,580 --> 00:14:10,460
Hayate enjoyed it a lot, too.

243
00:14:11,060 --> 00:14:15,430
Doing good things for other people makes you happy, too, doesn't it, Maria?

244
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:19,740
I understand you, so you should get your sleep.

245
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:22,370
I wonder if Hayate-kun's all right.

246
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:25,270
