250
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:37,690
I'll do him in and...

251
00:14:37,690 --> 00:14:38,790
Hold it!

252
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:39,250
Huh?

253
00:14:39,250 --> 00:14:41,060
He's mine!

254
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:44,850
You're the robot from the afternoon!

255
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:50,220
You're the nursing robot that came out
in episode three and got defeated by Hayate,

256
00:14:50,220 --> 00:14:50,940
Eight!

257
00:14:50,940 --> 00:14:51,540
Oh!

258
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:53,790
You know me?

259
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:56,470
Tama, how do you alone remember him?

260
00:14:57,140 --> 00:15:01,510
Hayate, unlike you,
who is sitting pretty on the main character's seat,

261
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:05,650
I'm watching this anime's opening every week to the point that I have it down solid.

262
00:15:06,190 --> 00:15:09,450
Because it's the only section where I am sure to show up!

263
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:12,780
