264
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:15,660
He doesn't have any show time in the show,
yet shows up in the opening.

265
00:15:15,660 --> 00:15:16,660
That's why I noticed!

266
00:15:16,920 --> 00:15:19,660
Eh? Was this robot in the opening?

267
00:15:19,660 --> 00:15:23,570
I haven't seen the kind people recently, either.

268
00:15:23,570 --> 00:15:26,540
So, time to get my revenge!

269
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:31,000
